"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"人为什么会活得很苦、很累、很烦？广造诸业则命苦，贪得无厌则身累；焦思苦虑则心烦。僧肇法师说：“扰乱出于多求，忧苦生于不足。”所以，想活得轻松自在，生活不妨简单一些，知足一些，这样就可以少造业，少攀求，少耍心机。有个词语叫“何苦”，就是劝人何必活得那么苦。～演莲法师\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/g2eWxvO07ttiz6bq1-hdL.jpg?height=1440&width=1080)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1637723383,\"title\":\"人为什么会活得很苦、很累、很烦\"},\"digest\":\"IImg8zpwPecj-tJuokDq_UIaphTB-dlNk9TECXZjz00\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x339f0eDD9e567A6444b5Bbe80eD5506d1ce8bF87\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"PpjYd77Kclofkww-P7-fyih_AJugMe9DxaATJhJiZNc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"wHKGqm9nYxaNZwUlV7t4pZUERNLj-FNikEGzEPK6Opo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"oVoTygW15j3dPXDy4M1rsmgqe5iUju76WqszHudVZR97_JeX763z0cd8swk84-z0Th4ufQ1tUfw1RKacI2iFYA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x3427fb611c6466a6937cac81da7110ae9b068c1f8e58bbfee7544d5dd327036e40fe61ac760d7d5811d4c932f577c4a7efb34e8a1d3700fa18a300c793fcdfcc1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"PpjYd77Kclofkww-P7-fyih_AJugMe9DxaATJhJiZNc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"wHKGqm9nYxaNZwUlV7t4pZUERNLj-FNikEGzEPK6Opo\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"IImg8zpwPecj-tJuokDq_UIaphTB-dlNk9TECXZjz00\"}"